node.text: I get roasted by the Roastmaster General, Jeff Ross, this Friday January 1st on a Special #GhostAdventures “Comedy Store” 10/9c on Travel Channel. node.text: Announcement: Hey everyone, I am so excited to announce that I have joined the new season of “Halloween Wars”, premiering Sunday September 19th at 9pm ET/PT on @foodnetwork and discovery+. During the entire season I take inspiration from my collection of haunted & mysterious artifacts from my Haunted Museum in Las Vegas to challenge the teams to create frighteningly intricate cakes that are as spooky as they are tasty! Get ready!
